{"type":"message","id":"82603e9c","parentId":"78a593db","timestamp":"2026-05-24T02:53:07.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"mcp吗\" - they're asking if this is MCP (the Sorftime MCP interface). They seem to be confirming or asking about whether the data I just showed comes from the Sorftime MCP.\n\nI should confirm - yes, these fields come from the Sorftime MCP tool, specifically the `tiktok_category_report` and `tiktok_similar_product` functions.\n\nLet me give a clear confirmation.\n","thinkingSignature":"e6365d2567cedfdd4009a10db978474054d83b6304c945a1cd1644d7268ca5d2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，上面这些字段就是从 **Sorftime MCP** 接口查出来的。\n\n具体是 `mcporter call sorftime-mcp.tiktok_category_report` 和 `tiktok_similar_product` 两个接口。\n\nTK VN 能用的接口就这几个：\n\n| 接口 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `tiktok_category_report` | 类目数据报告（返回类目统计 + Top50 产品） |\n| `tiktok_similar_product` | 相似商品搜索（按产品名搜） |\n| `tiktok_category_name_search` | 类目名称搜索（找 nodeId） |\n| `get_time` | 获取当前时间 |\n\n你要查哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20622,"output":224,"cacheRead":45516,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66362,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779591176088,"responseId":"06619b081a68781d8157284929d8b67a"}}
